                "32": {
                  "id": "32",
                  "speaker": "Lens the Journalist",
                  "text": "Sounds about right. They're not letting anyone through without the proper permissions - Lord Gortash's orders.",
                  "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Lens makes a quick note on her paper as she speaks",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "18",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "3": {
                      "id": "3",
                      "speaker": "Lens the Journalist",
                      "text": "I've been sent down here by my editor at the Baldur's Mouth Gazette to cover the chaos at the gate.",
                      "context": "NodeContext: Hint of derision - badmouthing her boss here",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "18",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "2": {
                          "id": "2",
                          "speaker": "Lens the Journalist",
                          "text": "He wants some fluff piece about the heroic Steel Watch keeping the mob at bay - whether or not that's the truth or not.",
                          "context": "NodeContext: Hint of derision - badmouthing her boss here",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "18",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "38": {
                              "id": "38",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "And what do you think is the truth?",
                              "context": "NodeContext: with a sigh - can't believe it's come to this",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "18",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "28": {
                                  "id": "28",
                                  "speaker": "Lens the Journalist",
                                  "text": "That the refugees here are desperate, hungry, scared people. They're no mob - they just want to be safe.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "31": {
                                      "id": "31",
                                      "speaker": "Lens the Journalist",
                                      "text": "I've heard the rumours - Absolutists marching from Moonrise Towers, whole towns felled by strange curses. It's no wonder they ran.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "4": {
                                          "id": "4",
                                          "speaker": "Lens the Journalist",
                                          "text": "Of course, I can't write any of that. My editor only releases stories his friend Lord Gortash approves of, and he's very selective.",
                                          "context": "",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "",
                                          "is_end": false,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {
