              "link": "2",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "24": {
                  "id": "24",
                  "speaker": "Lens the Journalist",
                  "text": "There was a skirmish a few days back - a band of Absolutists came close to entering the city. People started panicking, so the gate got closed.",
